description:
1) Mount iso.


2) Install game.


3) Copy all the content of the folder \&quot;INDRIT\&quot; to

   \&quot;C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Microsoft Games\\Gears of War\\Binaries\&quot;

   except \&quot;startup.exe\&quot;


4) Find in \&quot;C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Microsoft Games\\Gears of War\\Binaries\&quot;

   the file named \&quot;GearsTU\&quot; and install it


5) Find in \&quot;C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Microsoft Games\\Gears of War\\Binaries\&quot;

   the file named \&quot;GearsPC_TU3_Microsoft\&quot; and install it.


6) Now copy and replace the file \&quot;startup.exe\&quot; from the folder \&quot;INDRIT\&quot; to

   \&quot;C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Microsoft Games\\Gears of War\\Binaries\&quot;


7) Create a shortcut to the desktop , have fun.


NOTE : In the folder named \&quot;INDRIT\&quot; you will find an ICON too , just to replace 

       the ugly startup\'s



                            Gretings to \&quot;INDRIT\&quot;
